                <h3>Short-Circuit Evaluation with OR</h3>
                <p>PHP uses "short-circuit" evaluation with logical operators. For OR operations, if the first operand is true, PHP doesn't evaluate the second operand since the result is already determined:</p>
                
                <pre>###CODE_BLOCK_4###</pre>
            </div>
            
