                <pre>###CODE_BLOCK_5###</pre>
            </div>
            
            <p><strong>Analogy:</strong> The logical OR operator is like having multiple ways to get into a venue. You could have a ticket OR a membership OR a VIP pass. Any one of these will get you in; you don't need all of them.</p>
